sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (Browser)
    participant UI as React UI
    participant tRPC as tRPC Client
    participant API as Hono Server
    participant Router as tRPC Router
    participant Zod as Zod Validator
    participant ORM as Drizzle ORM
    participant DB as SQLite

    User->>UI: Interact with UI
    UI->>tRPC: Call typed procedure
    Note over tRPC: Auto-generated hooks<br/>Full type safety
    tRPC->>API: HTTP POST /trpc
    API->>Router: Route to procedure
    Router->>Zod: Validate input

    alt Validation fails
        Zod-->>User: 400 Bad Request
    else Validation passes
        Zod->>Router: Input valid
        Router->>ORM: Type-safe query
        ORM->>DB: SQL query
        DB-->>ORM: Result set
        ORM-->>Router: Typed objects
        Router-->>tRPC: JSON response
        tRPC-->>UI: Typed data
        UI-->>User: Render update
    end

    Note over User,DB: End-to-end type safety<br/>from UI to database
